      passage: `<p>On the morning of March 3, 2019, the researchers Nadia Farouk, Peter Lindqvist, and Rosa Delgado ______ climate data that had been gathered from several monitoring stations high in Ecuador's Chimborazo highlands. At midnight, the air temperature stood at 4.8°C at the station with the highest elevation, and it had risen to 6.1°C by 6:00 p.m.</p>`,
