      passage: `<p>Silvia Moreno-Garcia first fell for short fiction as a young child and went on to publish a great many short stories of her own, among them "Return" (2008) and "Water" (2007). Even so, thanks in large part to the runaway success of her 2020 novel <em>Mexican</em> ______ she is now best known to readers as a novelist.</p>`,
