      passage: `<p>Uruguay's constitution, adopted back in 1830, includes just two of the seven safeguards of press freedom identified by the legal scholars Ana Roth and Kwame Mensah. After 1960, however, such protections grew far more common, as seen in Kenya's constitution, adopted in 2010 and ______ five of these safeguards.</p>`,
